eristic lengths show a nonmonotonic variation with time, and simple\ncoarsening described by power-law growth is only observed if the domain sizes\nare much larger than the film thickness.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Apr 2008 17:22:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
